results.abstract: Telstar Art Gallery [TAG] is an ongoing series of gallery designs that aim to exercise the freedom of architecture design in the current pioneer age of web3. TAG-3 features a patterned, concrete skeleton, framing the windows that let in the natural light into the first floor. On the other hand, a white, exoskeleton encapsulates the entire second floor. This clash in characteristics is what defines TAG-3.

results.abstract:
Bonkerz Gardens Chapter 1, In the beginning, the Genesis. There were mere fragments, morsels, clues and codes like strange cave paintings appearing in abundance. What we see here is the first in series of immersive spaces from the Bonkerz Gardens world. 
Here is the creation, the genesis, the first glimpse into this strange place. It is a space for gathering in, for letting go and tripping out, a space like no other available in this thing some peeps are calling the metaverse.
results.description: In the beginning in the primordial soup of the underworlds was a strange place birthing  creation myths and creatures of the multiverses we know today. It was a hidden garden of mycelial magic, curious creatures and a place in constant flux and rebirth known as Bonkerz Garden
